reviewText: My 2 year old grandson is crazy about lg equipment, bull dozers, excavators, and back hoe tractors.  Plus trash trucks, and firetrucks etc.  This video shows them all at work.  He sits spellbound and enjoys them.  He watched it on a DVD player, while traveling.  Some of the dialog is rather corny and annoying for adults but he doesn't mind.  It's real life equipment not cartoons.They even have the thing that tears down buildings.  So I would recommend it for all little boys who are into that stuff.

reviewText: We have a few of these Mighty Machines DVD's and this is my son's favorite DVD.  He would watch it 24/7 if I let him. We'll pass a truck and he'll tell me it's a cement truck.  How does he know that from watching these DVD's?  It teaches kids more about trucks and gives them a love for what they enjoy.
